```html
<!-- BeerCSS dark mode toggle -->
<label class="switch">
  <input type="checkbox" id="dark-toggle">
  <span></span>
</label>

<script type="module">
import { ui } from 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/beercss@3/dist/cdn/beer.min.js';

const toggle = document.getElementById('dark-toggle');

// Init from saved preference
if (localStorage.getItem('theme') === 'dark') {
  document.body.classList.add('dark');
  toggle.checked = true;
}

toggle.addEventListener('change', () => {
  if (toggle.checked) {
    document.body.classList.add('dark');
    localStorage.setItem('theme', 'dark');
  } else {
    document.body.classList.remove('dark');
    localStorage.setItem('theme', 'light');
  }
});
</script>
```

With BeerCSS, add `class="dark"` to `<body>` for dark mode. Theme colors automatically adapt via CSS custom properties.

```html
<!-- Linear progress -->
<progress class="primary" value="60" max="100"></progress>

<!-- Indeterminate (loading) -->
<progress></progress>

<!-- Circular progress -->
<progress class="circle"></progress>
<progress class="circle primary" value="75" max="100"></progress>

<!-- Button loading state -->
<button class="primary" id="save-btn" onclick="handleSave()">
  <progress class="circle white tiny" id="btn-loader" style="display:none"></progress>
  <span id="btn-text">Guardar</span>
</button>

<script>
function handleSave() {
  document.getElementById('btn-loader').style.display = 'inline-block';
  document.getElementById('btn-text').textContent = 'Guardando...';
  // ... async operation ...
  setTimeout(() => {
    document.getElementById('btn-loader').style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('btn-text').textContent = 'Guardado ✓';
  }, 2000);
}
</script>
```

Para una app de finanzas, recomiendo una paleta **Confianza + Profesionalismo**:

**Colores principales:**
```css
:root {
  /* Primary - Azul institucional */
  --primary: #1565C0;       /* Azul profundo */
  --on-primary: #FFFFFF;
  --primary-container: #D6E4FF;

  /* Secondary - Verde éxito */
  --secondary: #2E7D32;     /* Verde financiero */
  --secondary-container: #C8E6C9;

  /* Tertiary - Azul acero */
  --tertiary: #37474F;

  /* Error - Rojo pérdidas */
  --error: #C62828;

  /* Surface */
  --surface: #F8FAFE;
  --surface-variant: #E8EEF7;

  /* Neutral */
  --outline: #8E9CC0;
}
```

**Colores semánticos para finanzas:**
```css
.positive { color: #2E7D32; }  /* Ganancias */
.negative { color: #C62828; }  /* Pérdidas */
.neutral  { color: #F57F17; }  /* Neutral/pendiente */
.premium  { color: #6A1B9A; }  /* Features premium */
```

**Regla de oro**: Azul = confianza, Verde = crecimiento, Rojo solo para pérdidas/alertas.
